      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> parsley</strong> and<strong> coriander </strong>roughly</p><p>Peel and finely chop the<strong> shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Trim, then chop the <strong>spring onions</strong> in half</p><p>Cut the <strong>red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon), then chop each half into 3 pieces</p>",
